eu.linksmart.caf.daqc.report
Class Data

java.lang.Object
  eu.linksmart.caf.daqc.report.Data

public class Data
extends java.lang.Object

Represents reported data from a Subscription, as part of a DataReport.

Contains the id of the protocol used to retrieve the data, as well as a timestamp.

The data is returned as an array of key-value Attributes.

Author:
Michael Crouch
